## 1. Purpose

The SSGPT6 Kids Research & Learning Center is a child-focused, AI-assisted education environment designed for:

- safe learning
- short guided reading
- voice interaction
- avatar-led teaching
- educational games
- team building
- hands-on science exploration
- automated progress support through the AI Sleeping Agent

This system is built specifically for kids and is centered on curiosity, safety, simplicity, and structured growth.

---

## 2. Core Vision

The platform is a children’s learning and research center where AI helps guide:

- 15-minute daily reading
- voice-controlled learning sessions
- educational gameplay
- avatar case-study teaching
- team collaboration
- science exploration
- early coding and AI understanding

The goal is not passive screen time.
The goal is active, guided, safe, educational engagement.

