## 4. Core Learning Model

The center uses a short-session structure designed for child attention spans.

### Daily Learning Loop
1. Welcome and voice activation
2. 15-minute guided reading session
3. Avatar teaching session
4. Educational game or simulation
5. Reflection and encouragement
6. Progress saved automatically

