## 7. AI Sleeping Agent Role

The AI Sleeping Agent is the automation layer behind the learning center.

It can:
- schedule reading sessions
- monitor completion patterns
- recommend next lessons
- detect inactivity
- trigger friendly reminders
- prepare avatar lessons
- generate parent summaries
- organize progress reports
- support research dashboards

The AI Sleeping Agent stays background-focused and child-safe.

