## 9. Research & Learning Tracking

The center supports educational research in a privacy-safe way.

### What Can Be Tracked
- reading completion
- subject preference
- lesson progress
- quiz performance
- teamwork participation
- voice-command usage counts
- game completion
- improvement trends

### What Should Not Be Stored
- raw microphone recordings
- biometric voiceprints
- invasive child surveillance data
- unnecessary personal profiling

