## 10. Child Safety & Privacy

This system must operate with a child-first safety model.

### Safety Rules
- minimal data collection
- consent-first model
- no raw audio storage
- no manipulative game mechanics
- no dark patterns
- no harmful content generation
- parent/teacher visibility where appropriate

### Child Mode Defaults
- safe content only
- short sessions
- high-contrast visuals
- simple navigation
- gentle encouragement
- no public exposure of child data

